snippet.title: Pusa Studios
snippet.description:
Your daily entertainment LIVE and in replay - creators' and celebrity interviews, game nights, and educational how-to's! 
    
We are a husband & wife team from Montreal, Canada. Professional photographer and videographer who go live to meet YouTubers, creatives, and viewers just like you! We learn more about human stories and connections and bring in our knowledge and experience of growing our audience together! 

Our live stream shows are currently on hiatus. Subscribe and ring the bell for all notifications to know when we are on next!
